            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_110wh' title='Col. 110WH &mdash; HC Deb 03 July 2002 vol 388 c110WH' name='column_110wh' href='#column_110wh' rel='bookmark'>110WH</a>
            People who take &#x00A3;9 million of funding from an organisation to fight an election, and win it, should, if they are sensible, expect the organisation to come knocking at their door&#x2014;and also expect that, whatever they do, it will be hard to satisfy entirely.
          </p>
